api_list.name: URL Backlinks
api_list.description: This endpoints provides backlinks against URL.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://backlinks-and-keywords-fetcher.p.rapidapi.com/seolizer"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "backlinks-and-keywords-fetcher.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
